history.text: Hello!
Hey. Batman Begins is a pretty good movie
I have never seen it! Who are some of the actors?
Christian Bale is in, he plays Batman. Also Liam Neeson, Gary Oldman. Some really good actors.
Sounds like a high quality cast.
When did the movie come out?
It came out in 2005.
Fantastic. What is your favorite part of the movie?
I really liked how they told the origin story, towards the beginning, it set up the movie well.
Is it scary?
I would say more dramatic than scary.
Does Christian Bale make a good Batman?

I would say most peo
ple think so. It got really high ratings on Metacritic and Rotten Tomatoes.
Rotten tomatoes is usually pretty reliable.
The movie seems pretty long, does it feel that way when you watch it?

Not really. You're immersed in the story. I really liked how they told me about how Batman became Batman. I never knew the stor
y.
Does it do a good job of explaining what happened to his parents also?

Yeah. In the movie Bruce Wayne is a kid and he is scared of bats. He goes to a play and the actors are pretending to be bats. So he wants to leave. And outside, his parents are mugged and killed in front of him and he ends up getting raised by the family butler.
So overcoming his fear of bats is why he is Batman?

Well sort of. After a while, the guy who murdered his parents gets out of jail because he testified against a mob boss. Bruce Wayne plans to get revenge on the guy but the mob bosses henchman kill the guy first.
That sounds crazy! So the vengeance on parent-murderer is his real motivation to become a justice-seeker?

Yeah it definitely is the start of it. He then gets yelled at by his friend who is a district attorney. She tells him his parents would be ashamed if they knew he was trying to become a vigilante. So he travels the world to learn how to confront injustice.
That's awesome! Then he has an entire arsenal of ways to defeat bad guys!
Does he have any sidekicks?
Well he gets arrested on his trip and gets taught by the guy who is leading the League of Shadows, which is a group he thinks is out for good in the world.
Who would arrest Batman??
Well he wasn
t
quite Batman yet
He was arrested for stealiung
stealing*
Naughty Bruce Wayne.
Is Robin in this one?
No. Then he finds out the League intends to destroy Gotham. He ends up saving his mentor after an accident and leaves the League He returns to Gotham and becomes Batman.
He starts to fight crime and ends up finding out that his mentor in the league actually ran the League and was the one who wanted to destroy Gotham.
It's pretty crazy.

uid2response.feedback: I didn't have a document to look at, but from what my partner said, it sure sounds like a good movie!
